      <section eId="sec_11_3_311">
        <num>11-3-311</num>
        <content>
          <p>Within a reasonable time before the tender, the claimant sent a conspicuous statement to the person against whom the claim is asserted that communications concerning disputed debts, including an instrument tendered as full satisfaction of a debt, are to be sent to a designated person, office, or place; and</p>
          <p>The instrument or accompanying communication was not received by that designated person, office, or place; or</p>
